Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Spring...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A warm breeze stirs the cherry\Ntree branches, and tickles my hair.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is April...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As of today, I'm a first-year\Nstudent in high school...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All righty, my wishes came true,\Nand I got into a co-ed school near my house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this moment, my heart is full\Nof anticipation for my new life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what high school's like?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For now, on this first day, with the sky so blue,\Nand the cherry blossoms in bloom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm somehow getting the feeling that\NI'm about to embark on a splendid romance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:50.74,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Little Sister"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At least...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what I thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's my first day and I'm already in a bind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, little girl, you sure are sweet!\NYou in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come have some fun with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-Whoa...\Nwh-what am I gonna do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I'm so scared! S-Somebody!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And since I went to an all-girls' junior high,\NI'm not comfortable around guys!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ugh... It's no good...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm starting to pass out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Knock it off, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see she doesn't\Nwant to go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!? Who the hell are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-Who...? Saved... me...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up to us and we'll\Nmake you sorry, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early in the day for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just chill, will you? Big bros...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh... but I can't hold on anymore...\NI'm passing... out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:04:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, you forgot this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You guys, I told you not to tag along...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Those guys are... R-Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the kid's passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, she must've been\Nscared out of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?\NI can't just leave her like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This uniform she's wearing -\Nit's our school's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These other guys were bugging me,\Nand he made a dashing entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yelling, "Knock it off!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, was he cool! I just know\Nit was fate that brought us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he carried me\Nto the nurse's office when I fainted...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, how kind and gentle is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that why you ditched me this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting around forever...\NWell, I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Fu. I never dreamed\Nanything like that would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you never saw his face,\Nand you don't know his name, either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think you'll ever see him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll see him again, I'm sure of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he was wearing our school's uniform.\NThere's no question he's here at this school...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not like I don't have any clues...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will we ever meet again? Next time I see him,\NI've got to thank him properly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:06:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! I'm going to be sitting here...\Nso we're neighbors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, huh? A foreigner?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only that, but she's gorgeous!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wonder if she understands Japanese...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Um... What is your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Paula. Paula McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She speaks Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Paula! My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no need for you to tell me your name.\NSince I'm not gonna bother remembering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What kind of attitude is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was just a little too cold...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What was that!?\NWas that a hand grenade!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looked way too heavy to be a toy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be that she's actually really scary?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! Speaking of scary people!\NI almost forgot something important!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It may be important\Nto search for that prince,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but there's someone else\NI've got to hunt down, no matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to find him or else...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! All right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, just wait till you hear\Nwhat happened after, it was awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me, what happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Really, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that guy's problem?\NThis is why I can't stand guys...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, it's her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry to make you help me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. It's on my way, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the color of your tie,\Nyou're a first-year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes! Um... And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are an upperclassman, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:08:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a second-year. If you have\Nany questions, ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know... I think he looks like\Nthe guy from this morning...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... No way, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The way she's acting, looks like\Nshe doesn't remember me at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, well, whatever. No need to make\Nher feel like she owes me anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna keep my mouth shut.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But to be honest,\Nyou really saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not really sure where\Nthe faculty room is and all... And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've set my mind at ease a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See, I went to an all-girls' school for junior high,\Nso I was a little nervous about going to a co-ed school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now I know that there are kind\Nand gentle guys like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, this morning, as well!\NA guy from this school came to my rescue...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? Well, I'm glad to hear that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What I'd really like\Nis to thank him in person,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the thing is, I don't know\Nwhat he looks like or what his name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were a second-year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually, it's both him\Nand one other person...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:09:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's another second-year student that\NI have to find... would you happen to know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard rumors that\Nhe's famous at this school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Famous? Well, what's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ichijo! Kyoko's been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So? What was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but are there any other people\Nat this school named Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm pretty sure I'm the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you that Raku Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The son of the leader\Nof the Shuei-gumi yakuzas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who, despite having\Na drop-dead gorgeous girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,has a whole entourage\Nof pretty girls at his beck and call,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and who's rumored to be running the whole school\Nbehind-the-scenes, thanks to his father's authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that Raku Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up, hold up, hold up!\NWhat kind of rumors are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Then don't tell me that just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, the reason you were so nice to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was one of your ploys\Nto worm yourself into a girl's favor, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How could you!?\NI thought you were so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, hang on!\NAt least hear a person out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have just one thing to say to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...try to go near my sister again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think you'd have outgrown\Nbears in high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so heinous! Heinous, heinous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the enemy of all women!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How was that my fault...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Ichijo?\NWhat was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onodera. Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Haru? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, don't you worry about a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm here,\Nyou're safe, all right? Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Haru Onodera.\NI'm Kosaki Onodera's younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Younger sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. So now we're going to be\Nsecond-years, huh, Ruri?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I get to be in the same\Nclass as Ichijo again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hmm, so the guy she\Nhas a crush on is named Ichijo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Come on... that's really mean, Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!\NWhat were we talking about again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Oh, so anyway...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hear that there's a really scary\Nupperclassman at your high school, Haru!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say he's the son of a yakuza...\NAnd his name is Ichijo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, that's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo!? Tell me more about him, will you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that I've actually met him,\NI can see it clearly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought,\Nthis guy is dangerous!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll bet he's totally playing my sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to protect her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's right. You did mention\Nhaving a kid sister the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to let you\Nget your hands on my sister, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Haru, what are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're being deceived!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NI've been hearing this commotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who's this? This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is this gorgeous girl?\NIs she half-foreign?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amazing... she looks just like a model!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey... could she be\Nthe drop-dead gorgeous girlfriend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The rumors were all true, after all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kosaki's little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? So you have a little sister, Kosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have something on you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Something on me?\NUm, what are you talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because otherwise, it doesn't make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A person like you, so drop-dead gorgeous,\Nso stylish, who seems so likable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With someone who's\Nso obviously a loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who looks so shallow\Nand unpleasant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It makes no sense at all\Nthat you'd be seeing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What...? How could say\Nsuch a thing, Haru? Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get that you're upset,\Nbut that kind of talk is uncalled for!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Chitoge, you tell her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so your name is Haru, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a sweet,\Ngood little girl, aren't you, Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Chitoge Kirisaki.\NNice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you care to join me\Nfor tea over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?\NWho might this girl be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is this girl?\NAnd hey, another beauty!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you,\Nstop clinging to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please, where's the harm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Listen, listen, listen, listen, Master Raku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this girl another one of Ichijo's groupies?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come now, you don't mind, do you, Master Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Whoa! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no... I mean, never mind that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-How can you just stand\Nin the middle of the hall
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There's no need to be so bashful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,without a care in the world,\Nyour arms around a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Listen, listen, Master Raku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but he's got a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're still but a mere child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is something that\Nyou must see through to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the face\Nof such obstacles as girlfriends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so long as you have love,\Nthere is nothing that you can't overcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Master Raku,\Nnow that we're going to be second-years,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,isn't it about time you discarded your\Noutmoded girlfriend, and switched over to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do offer a discount for switching, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about me like I'm a used car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? Is this person\Nseriously in love with Ichijo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I'm totally confused...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, Ichijo isn't quite the villain you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sister....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind of rumors you've heard,\Nbut rumors are just rumors, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, you're wrong, Sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're too nice, that's why you see him that way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all... after all, I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this person got\Na look at my underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of underwear\Ndo I have on today again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me... what does she mean, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Save your breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a nightmare. A guy like that\Nsneaking a peek at my underwear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my sister doesn't believe me...\NWhat am I supposed to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.69,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Animal Care – Looking for New Members
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Club activities, huh? What should I do\Nnow that I'm in high school?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:24.95,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Animal Care – Looking for New Members
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something called Animal Care!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Animal Care, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being surrounded by adorable animals\Nwho heal my soul... that might be nice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that guy doing here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go! Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, eat! Hey, good boy, good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This really sucks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do I have to run into him\Nin a place like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, why is he\Ntaking care of animals, anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:18:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going home! No way am I\Ngonna end up in the same club as him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Onodera's\Ngonna show up today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What... what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would be just the two of us right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then we could just head home together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! Well, not that\Nthat would ever happen, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're awful, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, crap! Did she hear me just now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But you're that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're trying\Nto make a move on my sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when you have such a beautiful girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's no doubt in my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're everything I've heard you are\N- a low-life piece of trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A person like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will never let you get your hands on my sis–
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,–ter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm seeing them up close,\Nthose bears are pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since we took\Na bath together, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brings back memories, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still mad at Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am! He saw my underwear again!\NThat's twice, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So unbelievable!\NI'm never gonna forgive that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself for even thinking\Nfor a second that he was nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo is a nice person, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, maybe today\Nyou didn't happen to see it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it. What makes\Nyou think he's a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not sure\Nthat I can explain what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess in a word,\Nit's how he can be so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? What part of that guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's always thinking about other people, and if\Nhe sees someone in trouble, he can't just stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He stops caring instantly\Nwhat's going to happen to him, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it makes that person happy, he can be happy\Nright along with her from the bottom of his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of person he is... Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know, I never asked you,\N"what is it that you love about him?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway! I really think you and Ichijo\Ncould get to be good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think I'll pass.\NI have no interest in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sister, you're just too nice...\Nthat's why you can't see him for what he is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought, I'll have to protect you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what was that you said\Non our way home about a prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never guess, Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I had a fateful encounter, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:20:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jeez. What a fiasco that was today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who knew she'd start to hate me\Nthat much... Guess I'm out of luck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today I'm just gonna take a bath and crash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I'll see that prince again?\NI wonder what grade he's in?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was tall, so maybe he's a third-year?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what kind of person he is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gentle, and someone you can count on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just hope I can find him somehow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that reminds me!\NI almost forgot that I had a precious clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch, ouch, ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another bruise there?
